OL,3,CCorrie/Emmerdale reduction: new
OL,4,Cprogramming possibilities
OL,6,GOn Tuesday I discussed the creative
OL,7,Gand scheduling implications of ITV's
OL,8,Gdecision to cut the amount of
OL,9,GEmmerdale and Coronation Street.
OL,11,FThe move does have potential benefits
OL,12,Ffor viewers.
OL,14,FBut it is also important to
OL,15,Facknowledge the implications of the
OL,16,Fdecision for production staff.
OL,18,FStatements have been issued by the
OL,19,Fbroadcasting union Bectu and
OL,20,Fperforming arts and entertainment
OL,21,Ftrade union Equity.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/7
