OL,3,CCorrie/Emmerdale reduction: new
OL,4,Cprogramming possibilities
OL,6,FIt is to be hoped that compulsory
OL,7,Fredundancies can be avoided.
OL,9,FIt is also to be hoped that the
OL,10,Fdecision to produce less of Emmerdale
OL,11,Fand Coronation Street frees up
OL,12,Fresources and airtime for other well-
OL,13,Fresourced programmes of quality.
OL,15,FWe still don't know what ITV plans to
OL,16,Fdo earlier in the evening.
OL,18,FMight the 7.30pm slot accommodate a
OL,19,Frange of worthwhile programmes such as
OL,20,FTonight and the Martin Lewis Money
OL,21,FShow plus some new formats?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
