OL,3,CCorrie/Emmerdale reduction: new
OL,4,Cprogramming possibilities
OL,6,FOr could this mean a further
OL,7,Fstreamlining of the schedule?
OL,9,FFor the sake of argument, might ITV 1
OL,10,Fmove The Chase to 5.30pm and run the
OL,11,Fregional and national news between
OL,12,F6.30pm and 8pm?
OL,14,FThe "extra" time in the afternoon
OL,15,Fcould be filled relatively cheaply.
OL,17,FIt must be stressed that there is no
OL,18,Findication that ITV 1 is planning such
OL,19,Fa move.
