OL,3,CCorrie/Emmerdale reduction: new
OL,4,Cprogramming possibilities
OL,6,FHowever the very real economic
OL,7,Fproblems facing the free-to-air
OL,8,Fchannels ` and therefore production
OL,9,Fstaff ` need to be highlighted.
OL,11,FAd revenue is in decline, less is
OL,12,Fbeing commissioned, costs in some
OL,13,Fparts of the business such as drama
OL,14,Fproduction have risen significantly.
OL,16,FThis means less is being commissioned.
OL,18,FMany who work in television are either
OL,19,Ffreelancers or on short-term contracts.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
