OL,3,CCorrie/Emmerdale reduction: new
OL,4,Cprogramming possibilities
OL,6,FWith less being commissioned, some
OL,7,Fhave struggled to find work or had to
OL,8,Ffind ways to make money outside the
OL,9,Findustry.
OL,11,FSome may find more secure employment
OL,12,Felsewhere and not return, even if the
OL,13,Fwork may not be so creatively
OL,14,Fsatisfying.
OL,16,FArguably, this sort of crunch has been
OL,17,Fcoming since the industry started to
OL,18,Fbecome more casualised in the 80s and
OL,19,F90s.
