OL,3,CCorrie/Emmerdale reduction: new
OL,4,Cprogramming possibilities
OL,6,FAnyone who has a permanent staff job
OL,7,Fin television ` with a pension,
OL,8,Fholidays and as much security of
OL,9,Femployment as most other professional
OL,10,Fworkers ` is enormously fortunate.
OL,12,FIt's because I am concerned for the
OL,13,Fproduction community that I favour
OL,14,Frelaxing rules on advertising time,
OL,15,Feven though I well understand how some
OL,16,Fviewers hate excessive ad breaks.
OL,18,FITV 1 must use the freed up resources
OL,19,Fand airtime for programmes of value
OL,20,Fand substance.
